ActHistoric Sites and Monuments Act
PrecisAppointment of JOSEPH L. ANDERSON of Calgary, Alberta, to be a member of the Historic Sites and Monuments Board of Canada, as a representative of the Province of Alberta, to hold office during pleasure for a period of five years, effective June 18, 2019.
